Subject: drm/amd/pp: Add edit/commit/show OD clock/voltage support in sysfs
Git-commit: e3933f26b657c341055443103bad331f4537b113
Patch-mainline: v4.17-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

when cat pp_od_clk_voltage it show
OD_SCLK:
0:        300Mhz        800 mV
1:        466Mhz        818 mV
2:        751Mhz        824 mV
3:       1019Mhz        987 mV
4:       1074Mhz       1037 mV
5:       1126Mhz       1087 mV
6:       1169Mhz       1137 mV
7:       1206Mhz       1150 mV
OD_MCLK:
0:        300Mhz        800 mV
1:       1650Mhz       1000 mV

echo "s/m level clock voltage" to change
sclk/mclk's  clock and voltage

echo "r" to restore default value.
echo "c" to commit the user setting.

